text: Oluwaseun Temitope Osewa is a Nigerian internet entrepreneur.http://ventureburn.com/2014/04/built-in-africa-seun-osewa-and- the-most-popular-site-in-nigeria/ He is the founder of Nairaland, a popular internet forum launched in March 2005, which was projected as the biggest African forum by Forbes. YNaija listed him as one of the most innovative Nigerians in technology. He was also listed among T.I.N Magazine's top 10 most influential Nigerian online entrepreneurs in 2015. ==Career== Seun started Nairaland in year 2005. ==See also== *Nairaland ==References== Category:Obafemi Awolowo University alumni Category:Yoruba people Category:Nigerian former Christians Category:Nigerian atheists Category:Nigerian technology businesspeople Category:Businesspeople from Ogun State Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Seun Osewa
